inance in 5-Year Strategy</h3>
            <p>The New Development Bank (NDB) has announced that its second f=
ive-year strategic cycle will focus heavily on AI-driven digital finance. The=
 bank plans to increase investments in digital economy infrastructure across =
BRICS nations.</p>
            <p>NDB is utilizing AI models to build real-time monitoring, risk=
 prediction, and sustainability assessment systems for its development projec=
ts. This integration ensures that large-scale infrastructure investments are =
