yrighted materials for AI training.</p>
            <p>This regulatory move aims to protect content creators and publ=
ishers from what the Prime Minister described as "virtual theft." Financial i=
nstitutions utilizing generative AI must ensure their models are trained on l=
egally compliant datasets.</p>
            <p class=3D"trend-summary">So What? Australia's strict stance on =
copyright protection could set a global precedent, increasing compliance cost=
s for AI developers and forcing financial firms to audit the data sources of =
their AI vendors.</p>
