n-inteligencia-artificial-san-luis-potosi/">Read more</a></p>

            <h3>Trend 4: Google DeepMind CEO Calls for New Global AI Regulato=
ry Body</h3>
            <p>Google DeepMind's CEO has publicly called for the creation of =
a new international regulatory body dedicated to AI oversight. The proposal h=
