ndation. The platform focuses on data provenance, auditability, and cryptogra=
phic verification.</p>
            <p>Mithra AI operates beneath large language models, creating a c=
ryptographic Single Source of Truth to validate enterprise data before it is =
accessed by AI. This is particularly valuable for highly regulated sectors li=
ke healthcare and finance.</p>
            <p class=3D"trend-summary">So What? As financial institutions fac=
e growing pressure to prevent AI hallucinations and data leakage, platforms o=
ffering cryptographic data lineage will become essential infrastructure for s=
ecure enterprise AI deployment.</p>
